	dprr:hasSecondarySource <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNotes "The list of senators in a dated inscription of this year (SIG3 747) provides good evidence for the names of a group of ex-magistrates, although it is not wholly conclusive because of the additions to the Senate by the reforms of Sulla." ;
